{"tid":2458663,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「連燈力」基金 呂布軍第二十一次股東大會，用錯方法惹怒蒼天，求上天原諒...","createTime":"2021-03-23T14:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T15:40:03.000Z","uid":149018,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0ae64e6dcaa1a65bf098d9e9fe8ecaa547106b31","tid":2458663,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"「連燈力」基金 第二十次軍議結算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sgDfLpS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgDfLpS.png&h=e925f674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVjR3bx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVjR3bx.png&h=83d373f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5jOZ8nk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jOZ8nk.png&h=8918a351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJOO5nN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJOO5nN.png&h=9c77b585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前「連燈力」大將 呂布剩餘<span class=\"red\">870.7</span>HP 累計虧損<span class=\"red\">-12.93</span>%<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」基金 第二十一波操作意見收集<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」呂布軍成立只為了股東日日有燒賣食，穩健投資，為燒賣舖進發。<br />\n<br />\n一軍為短期戰線Daytrade陷陣營，二軍為一周長期戰線赤兔部隊。<br />\n請諸將及軍師團註明兩軍進軍方向提議<br />\n<br />\n1. 本次軍議操作為ALL IN制， 收集此帖巴打軍師將領意見<br />\n2. 收集軍師兵士們之股票後聽天由命買入。<br />\n3. 一軍買入時間預計為盤中23:15。<br />\n4. 二軍赤兔隊無限期反省中<br />\n5. 一軍陷陣營賣出時機分為&darr;<br />\na. 到達預計賣出時間為盤前21:00、盤後07:45或開市緊急調動<br />\nb. 增幅到達7%將立即設下5%止蝕位保存勝仗<br />\nc. 10%止賺及止蝕位，若為QQQ 上下限改為3%。<br />\n6. 若陷陣營該次結算資金增長5% 隨機選中買入股票巴打派發Payme燒賣一串<br />\n7. 呂布將保留最終決定權<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UR2XWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UR2XWx.jpg&h=9062ad7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1</a><br />\n第二十次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2457862/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2457862/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"green\">呂布曰：對唔住！！奉先以後唔畫鬼腳了！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呂布大意失荊洲，武力100 智力<span class=\"red\">80</span>操盤，請絕對相信本將軍判斷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hMV9PTB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhMV9PTB.jpg&h=6de80dc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2ed7cbe9527d3f343f5f00e1475ce04d48aeb41","tid":2458663,"uid":379710,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:53:02.000Z","msg":"智力向下熔斷"},{"pid":"72b7650f3a508a77a940099b2d2cbda675eae190","tid":2458663,"uid":128117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:53:03.000Z","msg":"輸到連顏色都錯埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a24448a4ecce5f15f74ac2515f6ffbfd6a22eb2","tid":2458663,"uid":33674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ae64e6dcaa1a65bf098d9e9fe8ecaa547106b31","tid":2458663,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"「連燈力」基金 第二十次軍議結算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sgDfLpS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgDfLpS.png&h=e925f674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVjR3bx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVjR3bx.png&h=83d373f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5jOZ8nk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jOZ8nk.png&h=8918a351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJOO5nN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJOO5nN.png&h=9c77b585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前「連燈力」大將 呂布剩餘<span class=\"red\">870.7</span>HP 累計虧損<span class=\"red\">-12.93</span>%<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」基金 第二十一波操作意見收集<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」呂布軍成立只為了股東日日有燒賣食，穩健投資，為燒賣舖進發。<br />\n<br />\n一軍為短期戰線Daytrade陷陣營